claim.claim-text:
1. A secondary battery module comprising:
a unit battery pack having a plurality of unit batteries arranged at intervals;
a housing having the unit battery pack therein, and a heat transfer medium circulating within the housing for controlling temperature of the plurality of unit batteries;
a flow control unit in the housing and controlling the flow quantity of the heat transfer medium circulating between unit batteries of the plurality of unit batteries,
wherein the flow control unit has a plurality of openings for passing the heat transfer medium therethrough, at least one first opening of the plurality of openings having a first selectively adjustable size and at least one second opening of the plurality of openings having a second selectively adjustable size,
wherein the first selectively adjustable size is different from the second selectively adjustable size.
